These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, asparagus, blueberry, garlic
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, fuchsia, black, red
1. the person who likes black is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who likes red is the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far left##1
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who likes black and the person eating asparagus##2
6. the person who likes fuchsia is the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | blueberry | garlic  | asparagus | artichoke  |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate    | mirinda  | 7up       | soy-milk     |
| Color   | black     | chestnut | red       | fuchsia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, kiwi, tomato, blueberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, superhero, zombie
4 different games are played: go, monopoly, bridge, whist
1. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
4. the person playing whist is between the person watching zombie movies and the person eating blueberry##2
5. the person watching zombie movies is the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person playing go##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Food         | kiwi | cherry    | blueberry  | tomato |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | fantasy  | sports   | superhero    |
| Game         | monopoly | whist | go | bridge      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, sprite, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, van, scooter, helicopter
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, cricket, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person drinking mirinda##2
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea         | lemonade   | sprite    |
| Transport         | van | helicopter | bus | scooter |
| Sport   | cricket   | handball        | volleyball      | biathlon   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: nizzad-games, gardening, collecting, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, skateboarding, tennis
City: marseilles, nizza, hannover, rome
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to rome and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is nizzad-games##1
6. the person traveling to rome is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person traveling to nizza##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | dancing        | gardening   | nizzad-games | collecting |
| Sport         | skateboarding | cricket | cycling    | tennis |
| City     | hannover       | marseilles     | rome       | nizza    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, lemonade, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, gospel, soul, disco
House: modern, ranch-style, palace, gothic-revival
1. the gothic-revival house is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking fanta##2
2. the gothic-revival house is the person drinking tea##1
3. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the modern house is on the right of the palace house##1
6. the palace house is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
7. the gothic-revival house is between the palace house and the fan of salsa##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | tea      | fanta       | lemonade   |
| Music-Genre      | salsa   | gospel  | disco | soul     |
| House      | ranch-style     | gothic-revival | palace        | modern |

