.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, ferret, dog
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, fishing, gardening
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, poker, monopoly
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing poker##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person playing poker##2
6. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the ferret##2
7. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Pet    | ferret | rat  | lizard | dog      |
| Hobby   | fishing  | gardening  | baking | collecting |
| Game   | monopoly | backgammon | scrabble | poker     |

