.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, papaya, pepper, pomegranate
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, pony, dog
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, funk, indie, rock
1. the fan of rock is the owner of the frog##1
2. the fan of indie is the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
6. the person eating papaya is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the pony##2
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pepper  | papaya    | pomegranate | lettuce  |
| Pet   | pony | dog       | frog        | bird    |
| Music-Genre         | funk | jazz | rock  | indie |

