.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
City: venice, london, boston, prague
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, billiard, go
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, lizard, rabbit
1. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person playing whist is between the owner of the rabbit and the person traveling to london##2
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
6. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| City         | prague  | london | boston | venice |
| Game   | snooker  | go | whist   | billiard         |
| Pet           | hamster | lizard  | horse   | rabbit      |

