.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, milk, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, woodworking, writing
4 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, goat, bird
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the owner of the goat and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Beverage          | tea  | fanta    | milk | almond-milk       |
| Hobby         | writing | photography | chess  | woodworking |
| Pet   | goat   | bird      | mouse  | horse     |

