.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, coral, white, light-blue
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, snake, frog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, time-travel
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes coral is between the person who likes black and the owner of the rat##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the owner of the frog##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | white      | light-blue | coral | black |
| Pet         | frog   | rat  | ferret | snake |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | adventure   | comedy | fantasy |

