.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, raspberry, strawberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, country, rock, salsa
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, doctor, software-developer, designer
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the software-developer is the person eating garlic##1
3. the pilot is between the fan of country and the fan of rock##2
4. the fan of rock is between the pilot and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the fan of rock is the designer##1
6. the fan of indie is the doctor##1
7. the fan of salsa is the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry  | raspberry | eggplant | garlic     |
| Music-Genre   | indie | rock   | salsa  | country    |
| Job     | doctor        | designer       | pilot      | software-developer |

