.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, mirinda
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, purple, aquamarine, blood-red
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, firefighter, entrepreneur, librarian
1. the firefighter is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person who likes purple##2
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the firefighter##1
6. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice     | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Color      | aquamarine  | blood-red | chestnut  | purple |
| Job        | librarian  | firefighter      | entrepreneur        | dressmaker      |

