House: colonial, tower, cottage, townhouse
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hamster, pony, rabbit
1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who likes light-blue and the colonial house##2
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who likes apricot is the owner of the pony##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the tower house##1
6. the person who likes ivory is the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
