.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, hamster, mouse, fish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, vegafina, montecristo, swisher
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, ship, trike
1. the oliveros-smoker is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the ship is the owner of the mouse##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the bus is between the montecristo-smoker and the owner of the mouse##2
6. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the bus is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Pet           | hamster | fish | mouse    | bird   |
| Cigar   | montecristo      | vegafina   | swisher | oliveros |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus       | ship        | trike    |

