.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, soy-milk, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, mystery, comedy, musical
House: futuristic, colonial, craftsman, cottage
1. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is between the person drinking tea and the craftsman house##2
3. the cottage house is on the right of the colonial house##1
4. the futuristic house is on the far right##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee    | mirinda | tea           | soy-milk |
| Movie-Genre       | documentary | comedy    | mystery          | musical   |
| House      | craftsman  | colonial   | cottage | futuristic  |

