.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk, tea
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, brazilian, french, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, ambient, pop, house
1. the french is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
3. the malaysian is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the french and the chinese##2
5. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the fan of house is between the person drinking milk and the fan of electronic##2
7. the malaysian is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | hot-chocolate | milk     | tea   |
| Nationality   | chinese | malaysian        | french  | brazilian  |
| Music-Genre           | electronic      | house         | ambient | pop |

