.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster, rat, goat
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, billiard, bridge
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, subway, taxi
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
2. the person playing bridge is the person driving the roller##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is the owner of the goat##1
5. the person playing snooker is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Pet         | rabbit        | goat  | rat | hamster   |
| Game       | bridge | snooker | billiard    | mah-jongg |
| Transport   | roller        | subway     | taxi       | scooter      |

