.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, strawberry, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, camping, rock-climbing, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, country, techno, funk
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
5. the fan of funk is the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person eating watermelon and the fan of techno##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | watermelon | cabbage | asparagus | strawberry |
| Hobby         | cooking       | camping     | rock-climbing   | writing   |
| Music-Genre   | house | country | techno | funk |

 